name: GOLDEN KEYRING
description:
THE GOLDEN KEYRING

**50% OFF FOR A LIMITED TIME**

The Golden Keyring consists of an 18K plated Snaphook and Carabiner both covered in hundreds of stones. The Snaphook is fully functional with a loop at the bottom that swivels around for ease of use. The Carabiner is also fully functional, open it up and wear it with the Snaphook or rock it as a solo piece. Attach the Keyring to a belt loop or wear it as a bag charm or clip.

name: MICRO XL JESUS PIECE
description: The Micro XL Jesus Piece is 1.5 inches W x 2.5 inches L plated in 18K gold with piercing rhinestone eyes and a 28' inch Franco chain. The back of the pendant also carries an 18K stamp.
